  "description": "A nighttime panoramic view of a city skyline and bridge, illuminated with vibrant lights and fireworks. The foreground features a long, modern bridge with evenly spaced lights stretching across dark water. Beyond the bridge, a cityscape rises with numerous illuminated buildings, creating a dense urban sprawl. In the distance, a historic suspension bridge is visible. Above the cityscape, a burst of colorful fireworks illuminates the night sky, adding a celebratory and dynamic element to the scene. The overall impression is one of vibrant urban life and festive celebration.",
